# gst-launch-1.0 decodebin

> Automatically decode data.
> More information: <https://gstreamer.freedesktop.org/documentation/playback/decodebin.html>.

- Decode data to raw format:

`gst-launch-1.0 {{source}} ! decodebin ! {{sink}}`
